WEBVTT

00:00.939 --> 00:02.761
It is a sunny day.

00:04.002 --> 00:06.319
The Sun shines brightly.

00:07.532 --> 00:10.552
Then the Wind comes to the Sun.

00:11.691 --> 00:13.071
Hi, Mr. Wind!

00:14.300 --> 00:16.060
What are you doing here?

00:17.186 --> 00:19.146
I'm giving light to the world.

00:20.338 --> 00:22.856
Huh! Are you that strong?

00:24.023 --> 00:26.757
No. But I can warm the world.

00:27.940 --> 00:31.871
Hahaha! I can blow very strong.

00:33.117 --> 00:35.557
I can blow away the trees.

00:36.728 --> 00:39.480
I can blow away the houses.

